        "definition": "query_result(count(ozone_build_info) - count(ozone_build_info{component=~\"$component\",instance=~\"$instance\"}))",
        "description": "Hidden helper. Returns one value when the component/instance selectors are hiding instances; empty otherwise. Used to repeat (and therefore conditionally show) the filter-flare panel. The regex only captures a positive integer between the closing brace and the timestamp, so a difference of 0 produces no match and the variable has no values.",
